SELECT column_name
FROM INFORMATION_SCHEMA.COLUMNS
WHERE table_name = 'staff'
ORDER BY ordinal_position;




Use the following table :

staff[staff_fname,staff_lname,id,gender,mobile_no,doj]
quota[member_type,max_books,max_duration]
members[member_no,member_class,member_type,roll_no,id]
book_issue[member_no,accession_no,doi]
students[student_fname,student_lname,roll_no,department_code,gender,mobile_no,dob,degree]
faculty[faculty_fname,faculty_lname,id,department_code,gender,mobile_no,doj]
book_copies[ISBN_no,accession_no]
book_catalogue[ISBN_no,title,publisher,year]
book_authors[ISBN_no,author_fname,author_lname]
departments[department_code,department_name,department_building]

Use the following condition :

All tables are join using primary and foreign keys



